[[SECTION]]
TITLE: 1. Purpose

[TEXT]
STATEMENT: >>>
Defines the current implemented Streamlit UI, including tabs, Prompt Builder UI, advanced/manual pipeline buttons, Project Context UI, memory panels, Manual Memory Feed, Runtime Log UI, Files tab memory-history management, ChatGPT shared-link import UI, and Streamlit session-state boundaries.
<<<

[[/SECTION]]

[[SECTION]]
TITLE: 2. Scope and Boundary

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-UI-ST-ROOT
TITLE: GHOST Current Streamlit Workbench Scope
STATEMENT: >>>
This file is a draft child requirement file in the GHOST StrictDoc requirement tree.

It defines ownership, scope, and placeholder headings for this capability area. Detailed atomic requirements shall be migrated here from legacy requirements, implementation status, architecture notes, UML files, and code evidence after human approval.

This file shall not duplicate detailed requirements owned by sibling files.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-UI-ROOT

